column6: STARSTALKER Part 2 finds Nova and his fledgling Corps pitted against a threat from another dimension, forced to team up with the galaxy's deadliest bounty hunter, and coping with a blast from the past!
column8: | writer:Dan Abnett | writer:Andy Lanning | inker:Nelson Pereira | penciller:Brandon Peterson | penciller:Kevin Sharpe | letterer:Cory Petit
